Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' across all cases
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases where 'Completed + In Call' follows any activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Average lead time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases with more than one occurrence of this activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' as a proportion of total case duration
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to the next activity, excluding 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call does not occur

Name: Total elapsed time involving 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before reaching 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Resolved', considering only cases that directly transition between these activities without intermediate steps
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Median duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Duration variance of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' compared to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Time difference between the earliest and latest 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in a single case
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Comparison of average duration between 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'
